Requirements:
   Linux >= 2.6.26 (32-bits), any distribution will do
   GCC >= 4.2 
   Python 2, version >= 6 (Python 3 not supported)

To compile:
   make clean
   make


Setup:
   * Add the console/ directory to your PATH and PYTHONPATH environment
   variables

Running:
   To record:
      console/bdr-record

   To replay:
      console/bdr-replay
